item.title: I need help
item.dc:creator: @pker_franc0 pker franc0
item.description:
@pker_franc0 wrote:

hey what do you mean about spawn? spawn on your inventory? or spawn on the map?
o and to spawn monsters go to the very bottom of your autospawn.cfg and above the [ENDOFSPAWNLIST] add this:
spawn = [npc id] [XCoord] [YCoord] 0 0 0 0 0 1
try typing ::mypos to fnd out the X and Y coords while standing on where u want to spawn the monster o and u can always add more just make sure its above the [ENDOFSPAWNLIST]

well to spawn a d chain type this ::pickup 3140 1… this code is for 1 un-noted d chain or… ::pickup 3141 (the amount u want) (such as 2140000) for noted d chains… and the first number stands for the items id the second number stands for the amount you want to spawn
